			<p><a href="http://www.conradnewyork.com/"><strong>Conrad New York</strong></a> is a beautiful hotel in Battery Park City, about a 10-minute walk to the wedding venue (<a href="/wedding/venue.cfm">Grand Banks</a>). We have a wedding block of <a href="http://www.conradnewyork.com/stay/deluxe-suites.html">King Deluxe Suites</a> (it's an all-suite hotel) reserved at the rate of $259/night. To book, use <a href="https://resweb.passkey.com/go/SDWED0716">this link</a> and the access code SDWED16, or call 1-888-370-1936 and use the group code SDWED. The cutoff date for the hotel block is June 29.</p>
			<p>Other nearby hotels include <a href="http://www.wnewyorkdowntown.com/"><strong>The W Downtown</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.roxyhotelnyc.com/"><strong>Roxy Hotel</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/nycws-new-york-marriott-downtown/"><strong>New York Marriott Downtown</strong></a>, and <a href="http://www.sheratontribeca.com/"><strong>Sheraton Tribeca</strong></a>.</p>
